    "is_good_patch": true,
    "synth_pr": "\n## Title: Fix signed/unsigned comparison mismatch in M3AP MME management procedures\n\n### Summary\nThere is a signed/unsigned integer comparison mismatch leading to incorrect branch downstream of function m3ap_is_MME_id_in_list in openair3/M3AP/m3ap_MME_management_procedures.c. When calling m3ap_is_MME_id_in_list() the behavior is not what is expected. The issue may be in m3ap_is_MME_id_in_list or a function downstream/upstream of it.\n\nThis fix addresses the type mismatch by correcting parameter types to match the underlying data structures.\n\n### Changes\n- `openair3/M3AP/m3ap_MME_management_procedures.c`: Changed parameter type in m3ap_is_MME_assoc_id_in_list from uint32_t to sctp_assoc_t to match the actual field type\n- `openair3/M3AP/m3ap_MME_management_procedures.h`: Updated function declarations to maintain consistency between header and implementation\n\n"
}